Google 生态构建闭环，并提供了许多有意思的功能</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">支持根据设计稿一键生成预测性热图</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-top: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2075\" data-height=\"1125\" data-imgfileid=\"100003216\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f4a0114&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FicPso03ibEQdStFoEay8GneYI0M7GnDdsjFY7ayQFt6BkrROS2lmU9PwUJhhtzUHzCPWR5xxLAXhUboFfsqgf8Ig%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">原型演示</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：支持一键创建</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">可点击的交互流程</span></span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，方便快速产出 Demo。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开发联动</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：支持将生成的 UI 资产一键发送至&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Google AI Studio</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，无缝衔接后端逻辑开发，</span></sp